   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Lesedi la Batho Social Relief Fund, South Africa</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Lesedi la Batho (&quot;Light for the People&quot;) offers social relief and hope for people living in poverty-stricken, underserved areas of our community with little opportunity to improve their lives and become independent of hand outs. We believe every person has the right to basic commodities and the ability to provide for their children. The strains and restrictions of the COVID-19 pandemic devastated families who were already struggling - and they need a helping hand now more than ever before.</narrative>
  </description>
